Feature Request

Description:
Provide a clear and concise description of the feature you are requesting.

Priority:
Indicate the priority level of the feature request (e.g., High, Medium, Low).

Justification:
Explain why this feature is important and how it will benefit users or improve the product.

Potential Implementation:
List potential ways the feature could be implemented or integrated into the product.

Additional Information:
- User Feedback:** [Include any relevant user feedback or requests related to this feature.
- Competitive Analysis:** [Consider how this feature compares to similar features in competitor products.
- Accessibility Considerations:** [Discuss any accessibility implications or benefits of implementing this feature.
